text: The Evergreen State College is a public college in Olympia, Washington, United States. There are about 4500 students enrolled and it was founded in 1967. ==References== * ==Other websites== *The Evergreen State College Category:Colleges and universities in Washington (state) Category:Olympia, Washington Category:1967 establishments in the United States Category:1960s establishments in Washington (state)
